# TransitShield environment variables
#
# This project requires NO keys — the entire pipeline runs on keyless, public-domain
# U.S. open data (MTA / NY Open Data Socrata + FEMA National Risk Index).
#
# The optional token below only raises Socrata rate limits for large ridership pulls;
# it is never required to build or run the app.

# NY Open Data (Socrata) app token — optional, raises rate limits for large pulls.
# Free: https://data.ny.gov/profile/app_tokens
SOCRATA_APP_TOKEN=
